question: Formula 1: Will Red Bull collect the most points of any constructor at the 2023 Bahrain Grand Prix?
description:
This is a market on whether the Red Bull constructor team will collect the most points at the 2023 Bahrain Grand Prix, a Formula 1 racing event that is scheduled to take place over 57 laps of the 5.412-kilometer Bahrain International Circuit in Sakhir, Bahrain on March 5, 2023.

Constructor teams are awarded the same points won by the drivers who race in their cars. If, for example, the drivers earn 25 and 18 points, respectively, their constructor team will be awarded 43 points, which are the points won by both drivers combined.

This market will resolve to “Yes” if Oracle Red Bull Racing collects more points than any other constructor team at the 2023 Bahrain Grand Prix. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If for any reason the 2023 Bahrain Grand Prix is rescheduled to a different time and date on or before March 19, 2023, the same market conditions will apply. If the race is rescheduled to a time and date after March 19, 2023, this market will resolve to 50-50.
groupItemTitle: Will Red Bull collect the most points?

question: Formula 1: Will 17 or more drivers complete the 2023 Bahrain Grand Prix?
description:
The 2023 Bahrain Grand Prix is a Formula 1 racing event that is scheduled to take place over 57 laps of the 5.412-kilometer Bahrain International Circuit in Sakhir, Bahrain on March 5, 2023.

This market will resolve to "Yes" if 17 or more drivers are classified at the finish of the 2023 Bahrain Grand Prix main race. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

question: Will 'Creed III' gross more than $35 million domestically on its opening weekend?
description:
'Creed III' (2023) is an upcoming American drama/sport film directed by Michael B. Jordan. It is the third installment of the Creed series and the ninth installment of the Rocky film series. It is scheduled for theatrical release in the USA on March 3, 2023.

This is a market on how much ‘Creed III' will gross domestically on its opening weekend. The “Domestic Weekend” tab on https://www.boxofficemojo.com/title/tt11145118/ will be used to resolve this market once the values for the opening weekend (Mar 3 - 5) are final (i.e. not studio estimates).

This market will resolve to "Yes" if ‘Creed III’ grosses more than $35,000,000 on its opening weekend. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

Opening weekend is defined as the first Friday, Saturday, and Sunday of the film's release. Please note, this market will resolve according to the Box Office Mojo number under Domestic Weekend for the 3-day weekend, regardless of whether domestic refers to only the USA, or to USA and Canada, etc.

If there is no final data available by March 20, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET, another credible resolution source will be chosen.

events.title: How much will 'Creed III' gross domestically on its opening weekend?
events.description: This is a market group over how much 'Creed III' will gross domestically on its opening weekend.
